@payment_api = https://localhost:7252

### Health
GET {{payment_api}}/health

### Create payment
POST {{payment_api}}/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
  "amount": 50000,
  "orderDescription": "Test SePay payment",
  "customerEmail": "customer@example.com",
  "customerPhone": "0900000000",
  "successUrl": "https://example.com/payment/success",
  "errorUrl": "https://example.com/payment/error",
  "cancelUrl": "https://example.com/payment/cancel"
}

### SePay IPN
POST {{payment_api}}/api/payments/sepay/ipn
Content-Type: application/json
X-Secret-Key: replace-with-your-secret

{
  "timestamp": 1777471869,
  "notification_type": "ORDER_PAID",
  "order": {
    "id": "45674711-43d5-11f1-b21a-a6006ab65aca",
